{"tid":1467104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勿分化、勿捉鬼、唔篤灰、唔抹黑、唔割蓆","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T10:29:27.000Z","uid":60545,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"3a7c2361f83c37b1404cd2e01937b113ae4f214e","tid":1467104,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:05:50.000Z","msg":"記住呀！！<br />\n其中捉鬼實在太危險 亂捉鬼只會令整場運動崩潰 互相信任都做唔到仲點行落去呀？<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再亂話人鬼可以？因為太容易捉錯喇！我地繼續我地嘅行動 冷靜分析行動就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f017713918241f1e84cea840a50afa6ef0dbe39","tid":1467104,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f68788c4903976bff6a47c1fee3694b99360ac5","tid":1467104,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e18185ecbf98f73a460651159e0857f4cdff30a","tid":1467104,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a5576fc1435761be4e002c5a146e3eb5600cbe","tid":1467104,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\