,"msg":"本人謹此宣誓<br />\n本人作為義士不傷害記者，不傷害急救人員，不阻礙記者及急救人員工作，不任意攻擊一般平民及其財產，不使用酷刑。<br />\n本人謹以至誠確認。"},{"pid":"5940895479c4b30cb5de2e8014f5fbf641c280a1","tid":1467104,"uid":300745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:10.000Z","msg":"我都明白好多手足壓抑咗好多情緒好憤怒，但如果我哋最後變成同啲狗做既野冇分別，其實成件事好諷刺<br />\n<br />\n緊急，如果再有鬼比我地捉左做戰俘，應該點處理<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1465250\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1465250</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5ab7827545d5c06100609b3e393affd9cbd67de0","tid":1467104,"uid":215932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:11.000Z","msg":"推呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ee494b474cc97842592c67865e36122027abb3","tid":1467104,"uid":95160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:11.000Z","msg":"文長幫推<br />\n<br />\n機場圍人要屌 但唔該唔好灰唔好割<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466484\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466484</a>"},{"pid":"1ade4f9d70230accc4517d5ce2ff5d003f9bf743","tid":1467104,"uid":144483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3853c83c56305daaee5504e68775e56b0580b9d3","tid":1467104,"uid":275787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:17.000Z","msg":"（建議）而家要點樣補救/澄清示威者打記者/救護？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467741</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫推/討論"},{"pid":"6003b3f536c2c1fff7c2990012c8f7c6d630a3e5","tid":1467104,"uid":13349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:56.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">「我懇請你們不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。」</code></pre>"},{"pid":"9c27761ecd4f8c22d98070644924fd81f5612048","tid":1467104,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re