yle=\"color: red;\">不完美</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">可接受</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">會改進</span></span>"},{"pid":"47328d8d7373872d606b877691655d56739b7ea3","tid":1467104,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:14.000Z","msg":"推，當年蔣介石就係輸畀中共嘅分化，我哋今次都捱得過嘅話，將會迎接最終嘅勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567100e9c16443d020a4705834487f7ef6f6ae19","tid":1467104,"uid":278333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:49.000Z","msg":"捉嚟冇乜意思，留住佢都冇用，除非佢打人，衝擊，<br />\n但平時街頭勇武就要小心。<br />\n<br />\n今晚應該有過百隻警犬扮人帶風向，<br />\n又唔被人走，又煽動打人，<br />\n搞完兩壇嘢後，<br />\n無端端散咗好多人，<br />\n之前一直冇打記者同阻救援，<br />\n今日就出現晒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">核彈也不割</span></span>"},{"pid":"da917cf2098a84c3094f27cf5b6fab61d6b8e00d","tid":1467104,"uid":301361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c357b374035b6870d472f7e6aa5abd0ccc1741","tid":1467104,"uid":3841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:12.000Z","msg":"鬼一路都有<br />\n只係而家公開左有鬼<br />\n大家先成日凝住要捉<br />\n最緊要係大家要自己理智分析同衡量每一個行動<br />\n全靠咁多位手足獨立思考同埋無大台<br />\n呢次運動先可以去到今日<br />\n<br />\n我地同黑警唔同嘅係<br />\n我地會反省<br />\n未去到最後都唔知今日係咪會令到個運動輸<br />\n但我地絕對係可以不停諗點樣可以做得更好<br />\n<br />\n要團結啊香港人！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"97f399c77eaaaa652ed0c0ff72d6801adc929f78","tid":1467104,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89a1a3ae00973ff5ad47999caebf67cc2a42ca35","tid":1467104,"uid":144689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbcbe2aa96d3f30e6e161285aafa5ad610f